"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"President Trump said he was not worried after a shooting incident at an event he attended. The man arrested is named Cole Tomas Allen from California.\",            \"english_title\": \"Trump Not Worried After Shooting\",            \"translated_version\": \"El Presidente Trump dijo que no estaba preocupado despues de un incidente de disparos en un evento al que asistio. El hombre arrestado se llama Cole Tomas Allen de California.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Trump no preocupado despues de disparos\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The UK's maritime monitor reported four suspected piracy incidents off the coast of Somalia in the past week.\",            \"english_title\": \"Piracy Incidents Near Somalia\",            \"translated_version\": \"El monitor maritimo del Reino Unido reporto cuatro incidentes sospechosos de pirateria cerca de la costa de Somalia en la ultima semana.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Incidentes de pirateria cerca de Somalia\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Lebanon's Ministry of Health reported that Israeli strikes on Sunday killed 14 people, including two children and two women.\",            \"english_title\": \"Israeli Strikes in Lebanon\",            \"translated_version\": \"El Ministerio de Salud de Libano reporto que ataques israelies el domingo mataron a 14 personas, incluyendo dos ninos y dos mujeres.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ataques israelies en Libano\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"President Trump announced that the US canceled plans to send a team to Pakistan for negotiations.\",            \"english_title\": \"US Cancels Pakistan Negotiations\",            \"translated_version\": \"El Presidente Trump anuncio que Estados Unidos cancelo planes de enviar un equipo a Pakistan para negociaciones.\",            \"translated_title\": \"EEUU cancela negociaciones con Pakistan